We are pleased to announce that the School of Information Systems (SIS) has been renamed the School of Computing and Information Systems (SCIS) to project the expanded aspirations and role of the School beyond Information Systems to include computing, which encompasses Computer Science, Computer Engineering and Software Engineering.
&nbsp;
We look forward to an exciting new chapter in our mission to nurture more graduates who are trained in computing technology and practical solution development!
